The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Roger in final
                                                                                                                                   Roger in final
                      
	Basel: Roger Federer will meet Novak Djokovic in the final of the Swiss Indoor tournament here Sunday.         
	While top seed Federer easily beat compatriot Marco Chiudinelli 7-6, 6-3, Djokovic rallied from a set down to defeat Radek Stepanek in the semis on Saturday.         
	The second-seeded Serbian beat Stepanek, the fifth seed, 6-7, 7-5, 6-2.         
